bilingual.target: 这篇报导可能是正确的。
他们很可能几年前就结婚了。

bilingual.source: So that's presumably quite stressful for you.
bilingual.target: 那么对你来说可能压力很大。

bilingual.source: This proposal will presumably cause a lot of reaction.
bilingual.target: 这个提案可能会引起许多的反应。

bilingual.source: Presumably somewhere there was a pig infected with both forms.
bilingual.target: 据推测，有些地区一头猪可能感染两种病毒。

bilingual.source: The latter will presumably trade at a discount to the former.
bilingual.target: 而后者可能会打折扣与前者进行交易。

bilingual.source: Presumably we give them some guidance on the sort of thing we want?
bilingual.target: 我们可能要把具体要求告诉他们.

bilingual.source: He will presumably resign in view of the complete failure of his policy.
bilingual.target: 的政策彻底失败了，他很可能辞职。

bilingual.source: Web 3.0 presumably will be the next step of the Internet evolution.
bilingual.target: Web 3.0可能将成为互联网发展的下一步。

bilingual.source: The street was filled with water, presumably from a water main that burst.
bilingual.target: 大街上满是水, 可能由自来水管道爆裂引起.

yingyinNormal.en: Do you even know who Lady Gaga is? Presumably, the wife of Lord Gaga.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道人家嘎嘎小姐是谁吗？我推断她应该是嘎嘎先生的老婆。

yingyinNormal.en: What does she mean by involved? I mean, presumably the biggest part of your job is done.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她所谓的“参与”代表什么？你的阶段性工作已经完成了。

yingyinNormal.en: Presumably you downsized when you left your job and maybe when you ended your relationship.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你应该是在辞职之后，也许在分手后，换了间小房子。

yingyinNormal.en: Because usually, people who own something presumably like it more than people don't own it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为通常拥有某件东西的人，会比不拥有它的人更喜欢这样东西。

yingyinNormal.en: It actually presumably if you keep on doing, and you're being a better health over the long time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你继续这么做，身体会一直很健康。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, you're clever and you're pretty. So presumably, Clever Miss Stubbs won. And here you are with your pony essays.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你也很聪明很漂亮啊，想必聪明的斯塔布斯小姐胜利了吧，所以你现在只能在这读那些空洞的作文。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 大概是因为给病人开个处方很简单，很容易，然后就可以考虑结束病人的问诊，而不是做进一步的检查。

exam_freq_info.chinese: 大概; 很可能; 想必是

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
